content:
Unleash the power of data to drive better business decisions. Connect data sources, gain deep understanding of your business and customer data, and deliver timely, actionable insights and predictions to your teams within the context of their work.

Reports and Dashboards include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics for Experience Cloud, Tableau, and Unified Analytics Experiences.

Salesforce offers several tools to help you analyze your data and act on it. Reports and dashboards are built into Salesforce. Connect data and create interactive visualizations with CRM Analytics, a Salesforce-native tool. Tableau is a flexible analytics platform with cloud, on-premises, and desktop applications.

Create standard reports on single or multiple related data model objects (DMOs) or Calculated Insights, or build a custom report type on DMO fields and records from Data Cloud. Visualize KPIs and trends from Data Cloud reports in your dashboards.

CRM Analytics is a cloud-based platform for connecting data from multiple sources, creating interactive views of that data, and sharing those views in apps. CRM Analytics is a better way to distribute insight to business users so they can understand and act on changing information.

Tableau is a complete, flexible analytics platform with cloud, on-premises, and desktop applications for harmonizing, managing, and exploring data with interactive visualizations. You can combine and manage data from multiple sources, including Salesforce, in the Tableau platform.

With unified experiences in Analytics tab, mobile, and Slack, you can interact with all of your Lightning reports and dashboards, CRM Analytics assets, Tableau views, and Einstein Discovery models and predictions.

Einstein Discovery augments your business intelligence with statistical modeling and supervised machine learning to identify, surface, and visualize insights into your business data. It uses predictive and prescriptive analysis to predict future outcomes, as well as suggests ways in which you can improve predicted outcomes.
title: Unlocking Data Insights with Salesforce
